relation: Park in the light if you have night classes, is does get sketchy sometimes.
Our Baseball and basketball teams are both really good for being community colleges
There are always lots of events going on, sometimes youll just walk into school and something will be going on.
The cougar grill is where everyone hangs out. The breakfast is really good.
Study study study! do it every night reviewing everything you learned thus far, it makes things so much easier when test time comes.
